        shareIntent.setPackage(&quot;com.facebook.katana&quot;);
        if(shareIntent.resolveActivity(getPackageManager())!=null) {
            startActivity(shareIntent);
        }

this should work . On a side note always check for [`resolveActivity`](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/55676934/what-exactly-is-intent-resolveactivitygetpackagemanager-doing) or put `startActivity` inside try/catch block for an implicit intent . because if no app will found to perform tjis action your app will crash .

